script.name: plugin.stationmgr.run
script.sourceplaintext:
* ======================================== * Station Manager Run Script * ======================================== * Manages the homebased ships at the station to buy/sell wares * ======================================== * Author: Cycrow * Date: 2018/05/14 * ========================================
$MIN.RELVAL = 5000 $MIN.RELVAL.SELL = 3500 $last.wage = playing time $time.done = [THIS] -> get local variable: name='egosoft.stationmgr.wage' do if $time.done $last.wage = $last.wage - $time.done [THIS] ->set local variable: name='egosoft.stationmgr.wage' value=null $last.blacklist = playing time $unpaid.wages = 0
* remember what ships are doing what $using.ships = table alloc $table.dest.ware = table alloc $table.dest.ship = table alloc $table.returning = table alloc $table.wares = table alloc $table.dropoff = table alloc $table.ships.selling = table alloc $table.repairing = table alloc $table.noroute.withoutjump = table alloc $table.noroute.jump = table alloc $table.prevsector.blacklist = table alloc $table.prevrace.blacklst = table alloc $upgrading.ship = null $table.mining = table alloc $table.mine.minerals = table alloc $table.salvage = table alloc $table.salvage.items = table alloc $table.ej = table alloc $table.blacklist.add = [THIS] -> get local variable: name='egosoft.stationmgr.blacklist' if not $table.blacklist.add $table.blacklist.add = table alloc [THIS] ->set local variable: name='egosoft.stationmgr.blacklist' value=$table.blacklist.add end
$waits = random value from 7 to 11 - 1
$used.jumpdrive = [FALSE]
[THIS] ->set local variable: name='DEBUG.stationmgr' value=[FALSE]
while [THIS] -> exists @ = wait 6000 ms $last.update = [THIS] -> get local variable: name='egosoft.stationmgr.time' $time = playing time $i = $time - $last.update if $i > 10 break end
if is a new script version available [THIS] ->set local variable: name='sm.restart' value=[TRUE] break end
dec $waits = do if $waits > 0 continue
$waits = random value from 7 to 11 - 1
$MIN.MONEY = [THIS] ->get station manager minimum money $MIN.UPGRADEMONEY = [THIS] ->get station manager minimum upgrade money $MIN.REPAIRMONEY = [THIS] ->get station manager minimum repair money
$time = playing time $money = [THIS] -> get money $wage = 0
$DEBUG = [THIS] -> get local variable: name='DEBUG.stationmgr' do if $DEBUG write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='%s: doing station manager loop', [THIS], $wage, $money, null, null
$salary = 0 if [THIS] -> is of class Complex Hub $array = [THIS] -> get products if $array $i = size of array $array else $i = 0 end $salary = 15000 + ( $i * 5000 ) $i = [THIS] -> get number of resources $salary = $salary + ( ( $i / 3 ) * 5000 ) do if $salary > 40000 $salary = 40000 else if [THIS] -> is of class Headquarters $salary = 100000 else if [THIS] -> is of class Dock $salary = 50000 else $salary = 10000 end
$supply.stations = [THIS] ->get supply stations if $supply.stations $supply.stations = size of table $supply.stations $salary = $salary + ( $supply.stations * 2000 ) end
if $time > ( $last.wage + 7200 ) $wage = $salary $last.wage = playing time if $used.jumpdrive $wage = $wage * 2 $used.jumpdrive = [FALSE] end end
$unpaid.wages = [THIS] -> get local variable: name='egosoft.stationmgr.unpaid' do if $unpaid.wages $wage = $wage + $unpaid.wages
if $wage AND $money do if $DEBUG write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='%s: Doing wage, wage=%s, money=%s', [THIS], $wage, $money, null, null
$unpaid.wages = 0 $this.name = [THIS] -> get name if $money < $wage $wage = $wage - $money $array = create new array, arguments=$money, $money, null, null, null [THIS] ->remove money: $money, transaction object=null, page=[Page.Menus], textid=1104657, null, null, null, null, null else $array = create new array, arguments=$wage, $wage, null, null, null [THIS] ->remove money: $wage, transaction object=null, page=[Page.Menus], textid=1104657, null, null, null, null, null $wage = 0 end $table = table alloc $table[Credits] = $array [THIS] ->add trade report: start=$time, end=$time, trader=[THIS], buy table=$table, sell table=null $unpaid.wages = $wage if $unpaid.wages [THIS] ->set local variable: name='egosoft.stationmgr.unpaid' value=$unpaid.wages else [THIS] ->set local variable: name='egosoft.stationmgr.unpaid' value=null end end
gosub sub.UpdateTempBlacklist
* check any ships currently working gosub sub.EmptyCargo gosub sub.CheckShips
* if we have unpaid wages, then we dont do any mor actionos $unpaid.wages = [THIS] -> get local variable: name='egosoft.stationmgr.unpaid' if $unpaid.wages > 0 * if the unpaid wages are too high, then cancel the command if $unpaid.wages > ( $salary * 3 ) break else continue end end
* check for any mining $ships.table = merge tables, $using.ships, $table.mining, null, null, null @ $ships = [THIS] -> call script plugin.stationmgr.getships : Exclude Table=$ships.table Include Returning Ships=[TRUE] Only Docked=[FALSE] Role String='mine'
do if $DEBUG write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='%s: Checking mining ships, ships=%s', [THIS], $ships, $money, null, null
if size of table $ships $station.resouces = [THIS] ->get station primary resources if $station.resouces $i = size of array $station.resouces while $i dec $i = $ware = $station.resouces[$i] $ware.main = get maintype of ware $ware if $ware.main == [SSTYPE_W_MINERALS] if not $table.mine.minerals[$ware] $percent = [THIS] -> get ware storage percentage: ware=$ware if $percent < 80 gosub sub.FindMinerals do if $ret.Done break end end end end end end
$ships.table = merge tables, $using.ships, $table.salvage, null, null, null @ $ships = [THIS] -> call script plugin.stationmgr.getships : Exclude Table=$ships.table Include Returning Ships=[TRUE] Only Docked=[FALSE] Role String='salvage' if size of table $ships gosub sub.FindCrates end
* first check for any free ships @ $ships = [THIS] -> call script plugin.stationmgr.getships : Exclude Table=$using.ships Include Returning Ships=[TRUE] Only Docked=[FALSE] Role String='trade'
do if $DEBUG write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='%s: Trade ships availble: %s', [THIS], $ships, $money, null, null
skip if size of table $ships continue
@ = wait 100 ms
gosub sub.CheckBlacklist
$ship = get next key: table=$ships key=null while $ship * check for any ships to be repaired if not $table.repairing[$ship] $hull = $ship -> get hull percent if $hull < 80 if [THIS] ->should station manager repair ship with shipyards $money = [THIS] -> get money if $money > $MIN.REPAIRMONEY $flags = [Find.DockingAllowed] | [Find.Known] | [Find.Nearest] $max.jumps = [THIS] ->get max buy jumps $exclude.table = null gosub sub.GetExcludeArray $shipyard = find station in galaxy: startsector=[SECTOR] class or type=Shipyard race=null flags=$flags refobj=$ship serial=null max.jumps=$max.jumps, exclude=$exclude.array if $shipyard -> exists @ if not $ship -> call script !lib.player.saferoute : Destination=$shipyard Ignore Jump=[FALSE] Always Jump=[TRUE] Additional Blacklist=$table.blacklist.add Ignore Fuel=[TRUE] Allow Table=null $sector = $shipyard -> get sector gosub sub.NoRouteToSector @ = wait 10 ms else $ship ->set homebase to [THIS] @ START $ship -> call script plugin.stationmgr.move : Destination=$shipyard Ware=null Ware Amount=0 Type='repair' $table.repairing[$ship] = $shipyard $using.ships[$ship] = $shipyard end end end end if not $table.repairing[$ship] if [THIS] ->should station manager repair ship with HQ $hq = get player HQ if $hq -> exists $ship ->set homebase to [THIS] @ START $ship -> call script plugin.stationmgr.move : Destination=$hq Ware=null Ware Amount=0 Type='repair' $table.repairing[$ship] = $hq $using.ships[$ship] = $hq end end end end end
if [THIS] ->should station manager upgrade ships if not $using.ships[$ship] if not $upgrading.ship -> exists $money = [THIS] -> get money if $money > $MIN.UPGRADEMONEY @ $tUpgrades = [THIS] -> call script plugin.stationmgr.upgradelist : Filter Exclusions=[TRUE] Filter Ship=$ship
$exclude.table = null gosub sub.GetExcludeArray
$ware = get next key: table=$tUpgrades key=null while $ware $amt = $tUpgrades[$ware]
* first check if the station has it if not is equipment: ware=$ware $station.amt = [THIS] -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay if $station.amt >= $amt = $ship ->load $amt units of $ware, ignore minimum=[TRUE] $ware = get next key: table=$tUpgrades key=$ware continue end end
@ $destination = [THIS] -> call script plugin.stationmgr.findupgrade : Ship=$ship Upgrade=$ware Blacklist=$exclude.table @ = wait 20 ms if $destination -> exists @ if not $ship -> call script !lib.player.saferoute : Destination=$destination Ignore Jump=[FALSE] Always Jump=[TRUE] Additional Blacklist=$table.blacklist.add Ignore Fuel=[TRUE] $sector = $destination -> get sector gosub sub.NoRouteToSector @ = wait 10 ms $exclude.table = null gosub sub.GetExcludeArray else $using.ships[$ship] = $destination $upgrading.ship = $ship $ship ->set homebase to [THIS] @ START $ship -> call script plugin.stationmgr.move : Destination=$destination Ware=$ware Ware Amount=1 Type='upgrade' break end end $ware = get next key: table=$tUpgrades key=$ware end end end end end
* call ships home if not $using.ships[$ship] $cmd = $ship -> get command if $cmd != COMMAND_RETURN_HOME $docked.at = $ship -> is docked if $docked.at != [THIS] $ship ->set homebase to [THIS] @ START $ship -> call script plugin.stationmgr.move : Destination=[THIS] Ware=null Ware Amount=0 Type='home' end end end $ship = get next key: table=$ships key=$ship end
@ = wait 100 ms
@ $ships = [THIS] -> call script plugin.stationmgr.getships : Exclude Table=$using.ships Include Returning Ships=[TRUE] Only Docked=[FALSE] Role String='buy'
do if $DEBUG write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='%s: Ships availble to buy: %s', [THIS], $ships, $money, null, null
* for headquarters, we get amount wares for loadouts if [THIS] -> is of class Headquarters $money = [THIS] -> get money if $money >= $MIN.MONEY if not [THIS] ->get HQ current production gosub sub.HQProduction do if $ret.Done continue end
if [THIS] ->should station manager stock for loadouts $loadout.wares = table alloc $array = [THIS] ->get HQ loadout ids $i = size of array $array while $i dec $i = $loadout.id = $array[$i] $flags = [Loadout.Ammunition] | [Loadout.Lasers] | [Loadout.Missiles] | [Loadout.Shields] $table = [THIS] ->get HQ loadout wares: id=$loadout.id flags=$flags $ware = get next key: table=$table key=null while $ware $ware.amt = $table[$ware] $amt = $loadout.wares[$ware] if $amt $amt = get maximum, $amt, $ware.amt, null, null, null $loadout.wares[$ware] = $amt else $loadout.wares[$ware] = $ware.amt end $ware = get next key: table=$table key=$ware end end if size of table $loadout.wares do if $DEBUG write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='%s: Searching for loadout wares: %s', [THIS], $loadout.wares, $money, null, null $need.ware = table alloc $ware = get next key: table=$loadout.wares key=null while $ware if not [THIS] -> trades with ware $ware [THIS] ->add tradeable to dock: ware=$ware [THIS] ->change ware to storage: ware=$ware end
$ware.amt = $loadout.wares[$ware] $ware.max = [THIS] -> get max amount of ware $ware that can be stored in cargo bay do if $ware.amt > $ware.max $ware.amt = $ware.max $amt = [THIS] -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $ware.amt = $ware.amt - $amt if $ware.amt > 0 $need.ware[$ware] = $ware.amt end $ware = get next key: table=$loadout.wares key=$ware end gosub sub.BuyResouces do if $ret.Done continue end end
gosub sub.HQProduction do if $ret.Done continue
@ = wait 100 ms end end
* now decide what action we need to take $need.ware = null if [THIS] -> is of class Factory $table.stations = table alloc if [THIS] -> is of class Complex Hub $stations = [THIS] ->get factories connected to complex $i = size of array $stations while $i dec $i = $station = $stations[$i] $table.stations[$station] = $station end else $table.stations[[THIS]] = [THIS] end
@ $production = [THIS] -> call script !lib.station.getproduction : Station Table=$table.stations $prod.time = $production[0] $products = $production[1] $resouces = $production[2]
$station.resouces = [THIS] ->get primary resources table $need.amt = table alloc
$table.restrictions = [THIS] -> get local variable: name='stationmgr.restrict'
$money = [THIS] -> get money $next.ware = get next key: table=$station.resouces key=null while $next.ware $ware = $next.ware $next.ware = get next key: table=$station.resouces key=$next.ware if $table.restrictions do if $table.restrictions[$ware] continue end skip if $resouces[$ware] continue $needed = $resouces[$ware] if $products[$ware] $produced = $products[$ware] $needed = $needed - $produced end do if $needed <= 0 continue
$ware.price = [THIS] -> get price of ware $ware $ware.price = $ware.price * $needed do if $money < $ware.price continue $need.amt[$ware] = $needed end
$need.ware = table alloc
$time.step = 600 while not size of table $need.ware $next.ware = get next key: table=$need.amt key=null while $next.ware $ware = $next.ware $next.ware = get next key: table=$need.amt key=$next.ware
$needed = $need.amt[$ware] $needed = fixed multiply and divide: $needed * $time.step / $prod.time $amt = [THIS] -> get true amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $needed = $needed - $amt do if $needed <= 0 continue $need.ware[$ware] = $needed end $time.step = $time.step + 600 do if $time.step >= 4800 break end
else if [THIS] -> is of class Dock $min.storage = [THIS] ->get minimum storage table if $min.storage $ware = get next key: table=$min.storage key=null while $ware if $table.restrictions $ware.restrict = $table.restrictions[$ware] if $ware.restrict == 1 OR $ware.restrict == 3 $ware = get next key: table=$min.storage key=$ware continue end end
$amt = $min.storage[$ware] $station.amt = [THIS] -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $amt = $amt - $station.amt if $amt > 0 skip if $need.ware $need.ware = table alloc $need.ware[$ware] = $amt end $ware = get next key: table=$min.storage key=$ware end end end
* remove wares we are allready getting if $need.ware do if $DEBUG write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='%s: Priority 1, Need Wares=%s, Getting=%s', [THIS], $need.ware, $table.wares, null, null $next.ware = get next key: table=$need.ware key=null while $next.ware $ware = $next.ware $next.ware = get next key: table=$need.ware key=$next.ware
$amt = $need.ware[$ware] $ware.amt = $table.wares[$ware] do if $ware.amt $amt = $amt - $ware.amt
if $amt > 0 $need.ware[$ware] = $amt else remove key $ware from table $need.ware end end
gosub sub.BuyResouces do if $ret.Done continue end
* ============================= * Sell Products - Lots @ = wait 100 ms
@ $ships = [THIS] -> call script plugin.stationmgr.getships : Exclude Table=$using.ships Include Returning Ships=[TRUE] Only Docked=[TRUE] Role String='sell' if size of table $ships $need.ware = table alloc
$table.restrictions = [THIS] -> get local variable: name='stationmgr.restrict'
$station.producuts = [THIS] ->get products table: include equipment=[FALSE] $next.ware = get next key: table=$station.producuts key=null while $next.ware $ware = $next.ware $next.ware = get next key: table=$station.producuts key=$next.ware
if $table.restrictions $ware.restrict = $table.restrictions[$ware] do if $ware.restrict == 1 OR $ware.restrict == 2 continue end
$ware.reservered = 0 if [THIS] -> is of class Headquarters gosub sub.HQReserveWare end
$ware.amt = [THIS] -> get true amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $ware.amt = $ware.amt - $ware.reservered if $ware.amt > 0 $station.amt = [THIS] -> get max amount of ware $ware that can be stored in cargo bay $amt = fixed multiply and divide: $ware.amt * 100 / $station.amt if $amt >= 50 $ware.amt = [THIS] -> get true amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $need.ware[$ware] = $ware.amt end end end
gosub sub.SellProduct do if $ret.Done continue end
* ============================= * Buy Intemediates if [THIS] -> is of class Complex Hub @ = wait 100 ms $table.restrictions = [THIS] -> get local variable: name='stationmgr.restrict'
$threshold = [THIS] ->get station manager intermediate buy threshold $money = [THIS] -> get money if $money > $MIN.MONEY if $threshold > 0 @ $ships = [THIS] -> call script plugin.stationmgr.getships : Exclude Table=$using.ships Include Returning Ships=[TRUE] Only Docked=[FALSE] Role String='buy' if size of table $ships $need.ware = table alloc $station.resouces = [THIS] ->get complex intermediate wares $i = size of array $station.resouces while $i dec $i = $ware = $station.resouces[$i] if $table.restrictions $ware.restrict = $table.restrictions[$ware] do if $ware.restrict == 1 OR $ware.restrict == 3 continue end
if [THIS] ->can buy intermediate ware: ware=$ware $station.amt = [THIS] -> get max amount of ware $ware that can be stored in cargo bay $ware.amt = [THIS] -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $amt = fixed multiply and divide: $ware.amt * 100 / $station.amt if $amt < $threshold $amt = fixed multiply and divide: $station.amt * $threshold / 100 $amt = $amt - $ware.amt do if $amt > 0 $need.ware[$ware] = $amt end end end gosub sub.BuyResouces do if $ret.Done continue end end end end
* ============================= * Sell Intemediates if [THIS] -> is of class Complex Hub @ = wait 100 ms $table.restrictions = [THIS] -> get local variable: name='stationmgr.restrict' $threshold = [THIS] ->get station manager intermediate sell threshold if $threshold < 100 @ $ships = [THIS] -> call script plugin.stationmgr.getships : Exclude Table=$using.ships Include Returning Ships=[TRUE] Only Docked=[TRUE] Role String='sell' if size of table $ships $need.ware = table alloc $station.producuts = [THIS] ->get complex intermediate wares $i = size of array $station.producuts while $i dec $i = $ware = $station.producuts[$i] if $table.restrictions $ware.restrict = $table.restrictions[$ware] do if $ware.restrict == 1 OR $ware.restrict == 2 continue end
if [THIS] ->can sell intermediate ware: ware=$ware $station.amt = [THIS] -> get max amount of ware $ware that can be stored in cargo bay $ware.amt = [THIS] -> get true amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $amt = fixed multiply and divide: $ware.amt * 100 / $station.amt if $amt > $threshold $amt = fixed multiply and divide: $station.amt * $threshold / 100 $amt = $ware.amt - $amt do if $amt > 0 $need.ware[$ware] = $amt end end end gosub sub.SellProduct do if $ret.Done continue end end end
* ============================= * Buy Resouces 60% @ = wait 100 ms $table.restrictions = [THIS] -> get local variable: name='stationmgr.restrict' if not [THIS] -> get cargo bay size $ships.table = merge tables, $using.ships, $table.dropoff, null, null, null $money = [THIS] -> get money if $money >= $MIN.MONEY @ $ships = [THIS] -> call script plugin.stationmgr.getships : Exclude Table=$ships.table Include Returning Ships=[TRUE] Only Docked=[FALSE] Role String='buy' if size of table $ships $need.ware = table alloc $ware.perecent = table alloc $station.resouces = [THIS] ->get primary resources table $next.ware = get next key: table=$station.resouces key=null while $next.ware $ware = $next.ware $next.ware = get next key: table=$station.resouces key=$next.ware
if $table.restrictions $ware.restrict = $table.restrictions[$ware] do if $ware.restrict == 1 OR $ware.restrict == 3 continue end
do if is equipment: ware=$ware continue
gosub sub.GetMaxStorage $amt = fixed multiply and divide: $amt * 60 / 100 $station.amt = [THIS] -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay
$ware.amt = $table.wares[$ware] do if $ware.amt $station.amt = $station.amt + $ware.amt if $station.amt < $amt gosub sub.GetMaxStorage $ware.amt = $amt - $station.amt $need.ware[$ware] = $ware.amt $ware.amt = fixed multiply and divide: $station.amt * 100 / $amt $ware.perecent[$ware] = $ware.amt end end
if size of table $need.ware $need.ware2 = $need.ware $percent.array = sort table keys by value: table=$ware.perecent while size of array $percent.array $ware = $percent.array[0] remove element from array $percent.array at index 0 $amt = $need.ware2[$ware]
$need.ware = table alloc $need.ware[$ware] = $amt
gosub sub.BuyResouces do if $ret.Done break end do if $ret.Done continue end end end end
* ============================= * Sell Products @ = wait 100 ms $table.restrictions = [THIS] -> get local variable: name='stationmgr.restrict'
@ $ships = [THIS] -> call script plugin.stationmgr.getships : Exclude Table=$using.ships Include Returning Ships=[TRUE] Only Docked=[TRUE] Role String='sell' if size of table $ships $need.ware = table alloc $station.producuts = [THIS] ->get products table: include equipment=[FALSE] $next.ware = get next key: table=$station.producuts key=null while $next.ware $ware = $next.ware $next.ware = get next key: table=$station.producuts key=$next.ware
if $table.restrictions $ware.restrict = $table.restrictions[$ware] do if $ware.restrict == 1 OR $ware.restrict == 2 continue end
$ware.reservered = 0 if [THIS] -> is of class Headquarters gosub sub.HQReserveWare end $ware.amt = [THIS] -> get true amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $ware.amt = $ware.amt - $ware.reservered if $ware.amt > 0 $amt = get relvalue of $ware $amt = $amt * $ware.amt do if $amt > $MIN.RELVAL.SELL $need.ware[$ware] = $ware.amt end end
gosub sub.SellProduct do if $ret.Done continue end
* ============================= * Buy Resources - Lots @ = wait 100 ms $table.restrictions = [THIS] -> get local variable: name='stationmgr.restrict'
$money = [THIS] -> get money if $money >= $MIN.MONEY $ships.table = merge tables, $using.ships, $table.dropoff, null, null, null @ $ships = [THIS] -> call script plugin.stationmgr.getships : Exclude Table=$ships.table Include Returning Ships=[TRUE] Only Docked=[TRUE] Role String='buy' if size of table $ships $need.ware = table alloc $ware.perecent = table alloc $station.resouces = [THIS] ->get primary resources table $next.ware = get next key: table=$station.resouces key=null while $next.ware $ware = $next.ware $next.ware = get next key: table=$station.resouces key=$next.ware
if $table.restrictions $ware.restrict = $table.restrictions[$ware] do if $ware.restrict == 1 OR $ware.restrict == 3 continue end
do if is equipment: ware=$ware continue
if [THIS] -> get cargo bay size gosub sub.GetMaxStorage $station.amt = $amt $amt = [THIS] -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay if $amt < $station.amt $ware.vol = get volume of ware $ware $amt = $amt * $ware.vol $need.ware[$ware] = $amt end else $ware.amt = [THIS] -> get free amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $amt = $table.wares[$ware] do if $amt $ware.amt = $ware.amt - $amt
if $ware.amt > 0 $amt = get relvalue of $ware $amt = $amt * $ware.amt if $amt >= $MIN.RELVAL $need.ware[$ware] = $ware.amt $station.amt = [THIS] -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $amt = $table.wares[$ware] do if $amt $station.amt = $station.amt + $amt gosub sub.GetMaxStorage $ware.amt = fixed multiply and divide: $station.amt * 100 / $amt $ware.perecent[$ware] = $ware.amt end end end end
if size of table $need.ware if [THIS] -> get cargo bay size $percent.array = sort table keys by value: table=$need.ware else $percent.array = sort table keys by value: table=$ware.perecent end $percent.size = size of array $percent.array $percent.i = 0 $need.ware2 = $need.ware while $percent.i < $percent.size $ware = $percent.array[$i] inc $percent.i =
if [THIS] -> get cargo bay size $amt = get relvalue of $ware $amt = ( $MIN.RELVAL * 2 ) / $amt $amt = get maximum, $amt, 10, null, null, null $ware.amt = [THIS] -> get free amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $amt = get minimum, $amt, $ware.amt, null, null, null $amt = $amt - $got.amt do if $amt < 0 $amt = 0 else $amt = $need.ware2[$ware] end
$need.ware = table alloc $need.ware[$ware] = $amt
gosub sub.BuyResouces do if $ret.Done continue end end end end
end
* ============================= * ============================= do if $DEBUG write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='%s: doing station manager loop', [THIS], $wage, $money, null, null
$time = playing time $time.done = $time - $last.wage [THIS] ->set local variable: name='egosoft.stationmgr.wage' value=$time.done $restrictions = [THIS] -> get local variable: name='stationmgr.restrict' skip if $restrictions $restrictions = table alloc $ships = [THIS] -> get owned ships: class/type=Moveable Ship $i = size of array $ships while $i dec $i = $ship = $ships[$i]
gosub sub.FreeShip
do if $DEBUG write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='%s: Freeing ship: %s', [THIS], $ship, $money, null, null
$ship ->remove secondary signal: signal=SIGNAL_KILLED, name='station.manager' $ship ->remove secondary signal: signal=SIGNAL_ATTACKED, name='station.manager' $docked.at = $ship -> is docked if $docked.at != [THIS] $homebase = $ship -> get homebase if $homebase == [THIS] $restrict = $restrictions[$ship] if $restrict != 'none' do if $DEBUG write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='%s: returning ship home: %s', [THIS], $ship, $money, null, null @ START $ship -> call script plugin.stationmgr.move : Destination=[THIS] Ware=null Ware Amount=0 Type='home' end end end $ship ->set is being managed: on=[FALSE] end
